{"tid":458703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］九巴驚見慈祥外婆護孫竟然....","createTime":"2017-11-05T06:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T07:25:08.000Z","uid":139826,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99ca1549a93a77e851392fb307418387b8cdc810","tid":458703,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/144926_a736fb37e6d3e52d1773f49a684c38f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F144926_a736fb37e6d3e52d1773f49a684c38f2.jpg&h=d6bce31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n婆婆為咗孫仔訓得好啲<br />\n成個人坐丫曬  膊頭又則曬咁<br />\n坐得咁唔舒服都要就住個孫比佢訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時最多都係借大腿 要個細路仔訓落去<br />\n睇見婆婆咁愛錫個孫 <br />\n有種莫名嘅感動<br />\n推推佢 宣傳大愛啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bc414953ca0a7665d318ae28a6132c7d2179f0","tid":458703,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"雖然係廢老，但今次屌唔落"},{"pid":"f36028b51369cc428e89e10dcc0d1bd2973f1db6","tid":458703,"uid":130121,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母<br />\n有冇問人想唔想上鏡呀<br />\n咁又要比你放上網"},{"pid":"c47b81e593359616e7818639de4c145d39b28743","tid":458703,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然係廢老，但今次屌唔落</blockquote><br />\n好少見到咁肯就個孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83475de65222bdabfaaab36b93358f1f95538c6a","tid":458703,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"咁都要出人地個樣<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"612592a9f163aa2bde86694a5c41c5e267d597f1","tid":45